    <info>
        <title>Staff systems</title>
    </info>
    <para>To create systems of multiple staves you can extend barlines to join with the upper staff.
        To draw a <emphasis role="italic">grand staff</emphasis>, first enter a newline followed by
        a single barline <code>,</code> to start a new staff. To draw the brace connecting with the
        upper staff, type in <code>**</code>. Then continue with the clef and key signature as you
        would normally do. To connect the subsequent barlines, write a single <code>*</code> after
        them. </para>
